description: Boasting increased bass response and SPL output, Sennheiser's MX400 in-ear headphones sport a glossy black finish with silver print and chrome accents. The MX400 comes complete with a convenient black pocket-sized cord-windup carrying box. The headphones have a frequency response of 18 to 20,000 Hz and a total harmonic distortion of less than 1 percent.Sennheiser provides a two-year parts-and-labor warranty for the MX400.
title: Sennheiser MX400 In-Ear Headphone with Carrying Case (Discontinued by Manufacturer)
